**PRICE REDUCED**Charming 3 Bed, 2 Bath One-Story Home with Cozy Features! 
Welcome to your new home! This one-story rock and frame house boasts comfort, style, and convenience, making it the perfect place to call home. Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this property offers everything you've been searching for. Cozy Corner Fireplace: Enjoy chilly evenings curled up by the inviting corner rock fireplace. It's the perfect spot to create lasting memories with loved ones. This home also has a 2 car attached garage, as well as a storage building. Set up your appt to see today.
